From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ilies CHERGUI <ichergui@nvidia.com>
Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 00:00:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] PostBuildSteps: honor DESTDIR for install-time scripts

The install(CODE ...) steps in PostBuildSteps.cmake invoke helper scripts
(wrap_headers.py, embed_libomp_macos.py) with a path built from
${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX} but without the ${DESTDIR} prefix. Unlike
file(INSTALL ...), a custom execute_process() run at install time is not
relocated into DESTDIR by CMake, so with a staged install (DESTDIR set,
as done by OpenEmbedded and any packaging build) wrap_headers.py is handed
the literal "/usr/include" -- the host's include directory -- and tries to
rewrite every system header in place, failing with e.g.:

  PermissionError: [Errno 13] Permission denied: '/usr/include/EGL/egl.h'

Prefix the target paths with $ENV{DESTDIR}, matching how file(INSTALL) and
cmake_uninstall.cmake.in already handle DESTDIR, so the scripts operate on
the staged tree instead of the host root.

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: Ilies CHERGUI <ichergui@nvidia.com>
---
 cmake/PostBuildSteps.cmake | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/cmake/PostBuildSteps.cmake b/cmake/PostBuildSteps.cmake
index 71bd043..8149efc 100644
--- a/cmake/PostBuildSteps.cmake
+++ b/cmake/PostBuildSteps.cmake
@@ -21,7 +21,7 @@ install(CODE "
   execute_process(
     COMMAND \"${_python_exe}\"
       \"${_project_src}/tools/wrap_headers.py\"
-      \"\${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX}/${TORCH_INSTALL_INCLUDE_DIR}\"
+      \"\$ENV{DESTDIR}\${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX}/${TORCH_INSTALL_INCLUDE_DIR}\"
     COMMAND_ERROR_IS_FATAL ANY
   )
 ")
@@ -158,7 +158,7 @@ if(APPLE AND BUILD_PYTHON AND USE_OPENMP AND OpenMP_FOUND)
         COMMAND \"${_python_exe}\"
           \"${_project_src}/tools/embed_libomp_macos.py\"
           --libomp-path \"${OpenMP_libomp_LIBRARY}\"
-          --lib-dir \"\${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX}/${TORCH_INSTALL_LIB_DIR}\"
+          --lib-dir \"\$ENV{DESTDIR}\${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX}/${TORCH_INSTALL_LIB_DIR}\"
         COMMAND_ERROR_IS_FATAL ANY
       )
     ")
--
